Ah! Oh!

00:14.917 --> 00:16.963
Are you seeing any ghosts right now?

00:16.964 --> 00:18.472
No.

00:18.473 --> 00:20.889
Steve Myer is the mayor of New York.

00:20.890 --> 00:23.572
I asked him, I said, "yo,
what's taking so freaking long

00:23.573 --> 00:25.417
with the Second Ave. Subway line?"

00:25.418 --> 00:27.262
